overview: Rack City XXX is the story of Tyga's dream becoming a reality. Tyga's gold box has been stolen, as he tries to track it down in his hollywood mansion he slowly realizes that he is actually living his dream. Every room he enters and everywhere he turns he finds his crew smashing his maids, his groupies, his car wash girls, and his personal bartenders. Shit just got crazy!
title: Rack City XXX
